      "content": "i get that but i dont think a single glass of wine is really that much. i've heard people say a little bit of alcohol actually makes the meds work more effectively so u dont have to take a higher dose later. like, if i just have one glass and take the pill right after, isn't the risk pretty low? it's not like im getting drunk or anything.",
